gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Raptors 127, Mavericks 116
gameRecap.excerpt: The Raptors defeated the Mavericks, 127-116. Pascal Siakam recorded 31 points, 12 rebounds, and five assists for the Raptors, while Scottie Barnes added 14 points, 14 rebounds,  seven assists, and four steals in the victory. Luka Doncic tallied 31 points, seven rebounds, and eight assists for the Mavericks in the losing effort. The Raptors improve to 4-4 on the season, while the Mavericks fall to 6-2.
